Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:38.66,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(484,484)}For you…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:42.63,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(484,484)}あの頃のメロディ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:45.98,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(484,484)}もう聴こえなくても
